  "texts": [
    "The pros and cons of the ML algorithms further have been discussed in \"Instrument technology\" section.",
    "Fig. 13 Timeline of ML algorithms in fruit maturity",
    "Solar radiation/irradiance, water irrigation, fruits' positions in the canopy, nutrition in plants, environment temperature and soil quality are some external factors that have impacts on the fruit quality and maturity mentioned previously.",
    "These factors have been studied before but not extensively in relation to fruit maturity.",
    "Apart from that, the impact of season and weather on fruit maturity are well-known facts in horticulture."
